title: House Husbands - S03E12-13.avi
description:
House Husbands - S03E12-13

Lewis is jealous when Gemma goes on a yoga retreat with her childhood friend, Damo. Kane is heartbroken when Will's true colours are revealed. When Abi is injured by a violent patient, Mark is forced to change his career plans. Gemma and Lewis rediscover the meaning of love at Phoebe and Ryan's wedding. Kane finds his Mr Right in the most unlikely place: the school library. Justin has a chance romantic encounter that shocks the community.
